high_descs: Turn and go to the cabinet.
Pick up the rag on the cabinet.
Turn and go to the cabinet.
Put the rag in the drawer of the cabinet.
Turn and go to the bathtub.
Pick up the rag in the bathtub.
Turn around and go to the cabinet.
Put the rag in the drawer of the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put two rags in the drawer in the cabinet.

high_descs: Go the bathroom cabinet
Pick up a towel from the bathroom cabinet
Turn and open a cabinet drawer
Place the towel in the cabinet drawer
Close the drawer and move to the bath tub
Pick up a towel from the bath tub
Go to the bathroom cabinet
Open the same drawer and place the towel in with the other one
anns.task_desc: Place two towels in a bathroom drawer

high_descs: Walk to the middle of the counter in front of you.
Pick up the pink rag behind the bar of soap.
Move back from the counter to face the drawers below the counter.
Open the bottom drawer below the counter with the bar of soap, put the rag in the drawer, close the drawer.
Turn right and face the foot of the tub.
Pick up the pink rag from the tub.
Turn around and walk back to the counter with the bar of soap on it.
Open the same bottom drawer under the counter with the bar of soap on it, put the rag in the drawer, and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: To move two rags to the bottom drawer.
